The paper discusses the use of ASP solvers for query answering in a large knowledge base containing biological knowledge. This topic falls under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of logic programming (cs.PL) and the challenges faced by current ASP solvers (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the structure of the knowledge base, which could be relevant to the sub-category of logic and verification (cs.LO).
